Package model

Class Model

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Model
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EndModel, EstuaryModel, QuizModel, ResearchModel, TitleModel

    public abstract class Model
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This is the abstract Model class which all the models extend, this includes attributes that every model must have like dimmensions, time, GameObjects, and CodeListener
    Author:
    Miguel Fuentes, W Mathieu Mimms-Boyce, Devon Pirestani
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
